provisions.title: Section 1
provisions.content:
1. This Order may be cited as the Judicature (Family Court) (St.
James, Hanover and Westmoreland Region) Order. 1996.

provisions.title: Section 2
provisions.content:
2. There is hereby established a Family Court, to be known as the
Family Court-St. James. Hanover and Westmoreland Region, for
the parishes of St. James. Hanover and Westmoreland.

provisions.title: Section 3
provisions.content:
3. The provisions of seotion 11 of the Act shaII apply to such Court
with effect from the 1st day of April. 1996.
